{"tid":1811092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（突發）中聯辦主任王志民被炒魷魚","createTime":"2020-01-04T11:33:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T13:34:57.000Z","uid":125168,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9016a355cbcb147475eed91ae3a2dcae3ba8e30a","tid":1811092,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:33:10.000Z","msg":"[突發]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E6OGJsg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE6OGJsg.jpg&h=1024fa80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾經明示要與中環的林鄭「行埋」的中聯辦主任王志民, 被免去香港中聯辦主任職務。 據新華社報道，國務院免去王志民的中央人民政府駐香港特別行政區聯絡辦公室主任職務，並由全國人大財政經濟委員會副主任委員駱惠寧接任。 <br />\n<br />\n新任中聯辦主任駱惠寧過往未曾涉足港澳事務, 亦不從屬港澳辦, 今次空降該位, 反映習近平可能不信任現有港澳系統的通報機制欺上瞞下及報喜不報憂的作風, 今次拿掉王志民, 是打響整肅港澳系統的第一槍, 相信「人頭落地」的官員陸續有來。<br />\n<br />\n#綜合報導  #資料圖片"},{"pid":"bcc71045c8c3568ee2360d18c300bede1c5948b2","tid":1811092,"uid":34514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:33:45.000Z","msg":"依家要多啲文宣呀! 有新玩法 仲有教學同示範tim!<br />\n<br />\n[行動]文宣都十八區開花 A4 label周圍貼 (更新:大量現成圖 即print 即貼!)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810856\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810856</a>"},{"pid":"cba3326b1b7b4f6652a8572f5b29ef040399c34f","tid":1811092,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:34:00.000Z","msg":"source 本土新聞tg @localpresshk"},{"pid":"89b16e431091464b0773bfafdde17e8fcf9ee5ad","tid":1811092,"uid":255980,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T11:34:56.000Z","msg":"行得太埋之後暴斃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea5e79c291347a3e0188ca4b62ad3102788f8721","tid":1811092,"uid":41458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1